Text Cleaning (1 pt)

Load the tidytext package. Please define the following function clean_text() and apply it to digital$Skills_EN, store the result as digital$Skills_EN_clean. Check the details for your interest. It removes digits, punctuation, whitespaces and sets everything to lower case.

library(tidytext)

# text cleaning
clean_text <- function(x) {
  x %>%
    # Remove digits
    str_remove_all("[:digit:]") %>%
    # Remove punctuation
    str_remove_all("[[:punct:]]") %>%
    # Make everything lowercase
    str_to_lower() %>%
    # Remove any trailing whitespace around the text
    str_trim("both")
}
